data.description: ''Discover the perfect blend of comfort and location with this inviting 2-bedroom, 2-bath condo situated near the scenic Palm Harbor Golf Course. The upper-floor unit boasts a charming screened patio, offering a serene retreat surrounded by mature trees for added privacy. Enjoy the proximity to the stunning beaches of Flagler and surrounding counties, making this residence an ideal haven. This condo comes complete with a clubhouse that features amenities such as a heated pool, sauna, and tennis courts - creating an oasis for relaxation and recreation. The entertainment options extend to a pool table, ensuring endless enjoyment for residents. ''Embrace the tranquility of waterfront living with leisurely strolls along the Intracoastal waterways. This unique feature allows residents to connect with nature, offering serene moments and the opportunity to witness the beauty of marine life. Immerse yourself in the soothing ambiance, making every stroll a delightful experience that adds an extra layer of charm to this already appealing home."
